name: DentalIndicationsSurroundingAdministrationOfMedicationsToTreatOsteoporosisInMen
title: Dental indications surrounding administration of medications to treat osteoporosis in men
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values focuses on dental indications prior to or when administering medications for osteoporosis to men during urology care.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify dental indications when medications for osteoporosis are being considered or during their administration.),(Inclusion Criteria: osteonecrosis of the jaw),(Exclusion Criteria: none)
